metadata.name: 暁/AKATSUKI
metadata.description:
This is the first NFT work of the Collaboration Line.

”暁 / AKATSUKI”
 is Japanese Traditional Words, that means “dawn”.

This artwork is Collaborative NFT between Photographer まちゅばら │ machu.eth（@mpmb7）and Illustrator くろつき │KUROTSUKI（@kurotsuki_962）

This work and its counterpart "黄昏 / TASOGARE" are listed by Kurotsuki.

Two worlds, Two times and The twin girls.
In the dreamlike world reflected by the filter,what will twins think and what will they see…?
